column1: The tadpole has a different breathing method compared to the adult frog. Explain why this is so.
The tadpole lives underwater but a frog lives on both land and water.
The tadpole lives in water but the frog besides living underwater lives on land.
The tadpole lives on both land and in water but the frog only lives in water
the tadpole is idiotic but the frog is moronic
